    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Speedy and simple, this stir-fry is a mid-week winner. You'll sizzle minced pork, green beans and onion in a rich umami-packed black bean and sesame sauce. Serve with fluffy white rice on the side and dig in.",
